init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: One day I am called to a village to treat a patient.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I have no medicine with me, but I try to make the patient comfortable and wait for him to get well.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I leave the patient behind and continue my journey.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I was sad, thinking that the patient will not be able to afford it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I returned to the village and gave the medicine to the patient.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The patient was very thankful and promised to pay me back.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I left the village and continued on with my journey.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I was called to another village for work.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I was still thinking about the patient from the previous day.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But I decided to treat the woman anyway.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I treated her for a few days, and the woman started feeling better.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "You can keep this as a reward.
